item.title: CVE-2020-5681|2024-08-04T08:39:25.694Z -- seiko%20epson%20corporation -- epsonnet%20setupmanager%20and%20offirio%20synergyware%20printdirector
item.description: Untrusted search path vulnerability in self-extracting files created by EpsonNet SetupManager versions 2.2.14 and earlier, and Offirio SynergyWare PrintDirector versions 1.6x/1.6y and earlier allows an attacker to gain privileges via a Trojan horse DLL in an unspecified directory.
